      "side": 1,
      "message": "[🔴 Critical Issues - Must fix before merge] Line 2072: clearBodyOverwrites() clears pluginData but leaves previously injected \"bodyOverwrite\" entries inside SwarmMessage::editions. The emitted message is copied directly from quickAccess, so clients can continue displaying stale overwritten edition bodies after plugins are disabled/reloaded. Clear bodyOverwrite from each edition entry or build the signal message through the same injection path that erases stale edition fields.\n\n```suggestion\nfor (auto\u0026 edition : msg-\u003eeditions) {\n    edition.erase(\"bodyOverwrite\");\n}\n```\nApply this while holding loadedHistory_.mutex before collecting messages to emit.",
      "revId": "bab93ce252d97db9d447f464eaf48b50ac6aca00",
